// Embed the application manifest.
// This activates comctl32 v6 (required for TaskDialogIndirect) and
// declares DPI awareness so Windows does not DPI-virtualize the process.
// 24 = RT_MANIFEST  (numeric value used for windres/MinGW compatibility)
1 24 "app.manifest"
